Kristin

Not bringing anyone down here! If it were all in your head then you 
can put over half this group on the cookoo list with ya and I&#39;d be 
right at the top of the list in the straightjacket =) I think you 
will find most here have lost someone. Some more recently than 
others. Some more pained by thier loss than anyone can imagine. Often 
its the inspiration for taking notice of whats important in life and 
where we go afterwards. I find the work very comforting and very 
educational. Ive lost too many to count but now I only grieve for 
myself, mourn my own feeling of loss because I know they still exist 
and they are still around. Just in a different fashion than I was 
used to.

Misty

